{"type":"message","id":"277fbd46","parentId":"fe1ca64f","timestamp":"2026-07-08T02:26:28.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"不是，算一下：\n\n**Δ 分解：**\n- `|R/G - 1| = |130.9/33.1 - 1| = 2.95`\n- `|B/G - 1| = |8/33.1 - 1| = 0.76`\n- 合计：2.95 + 0.76 = **3.71** ✓\n\n**B/G = 8/33.1 ≈ 0.24，离1差很远。**\n\nB 在 fine 阶段一直卡在 21 不动，原因是算法计算 `int(g_sum/b_sum * current_blue)`：\n- g_sum/b_sum ≈ 33.1/8 = **4.14**\n- `int(4.14 × 21) = 86`，调整量 = 86 - 21 = **65**\n- 但 step=1，被 clamp 到 +1，所以 cb = 22\n- 然后 `|B/G|` 变大，`_eval` 反而变差，又被拉回 21\n\n**根本问题**：`g_sum/b_sum` 比例太大（4:1），而 fine 阶段步长只有1，每次只能挪1个单位，根本追不上 4 倍的比例差。算法在 B 方向陷入了\"前进一步、后退一步\"的死循环。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":320,"cacheRead":46515,"cacheWrite":857,"totalTokens":47698,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783477577590,"responseId":"msg_c62d3f59-c0c8-4c64-83fb-8326245bf35e"}}
