{"type":"message","id":"4c5caef0","parentId":"47a6f336","timestamp":"2026-07-08T02:32:57.770Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a concise summary of what I found regarding why B stays at 21. Let me provide a very brief, clear summary.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"B卡在21是因为算法每步只调一个通道，而R的梯度（0.042）是B的3.6倍（0.012），所以贪心策略永远选调R。39步全在降R，B从未被选中。\n\n**根因**：`_eval`公式对R/B梯度不对称，R离目标远但当前增益大→梯度大；B离目标远但当前增益小→梯度小。贪心算法只追最大梯度，B被饿死。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":57105,"output":131,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57236,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783477966674,"responseId":"cht000dea35@dx19f3f922d8d29c2503"}}
