{"type":"message","id":"9b9ad993","parentId":"4f1cd9b8","timestamp":"2026-07-08T02:54:16.518Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to redesign the white balance algorithm. Let me summarize what I've done:\n\n1. ✅ Backed up original whitebalance.py to `backup_20260708_wb_redesign/whitebalance.py.bak`\n2. ✅ Rewrote IterativeWB class with:\n   - Dynamic step size: delta > 10 → 5, 1 < delta <= 10 → 2, delta <= 1 → 1\n   - No step limits\n   - Oscillation detection: at step=1, 3 consecutive no-improvement → restore best and stop\n   - Simplified the algorithm (removed complex state machine)\n3. ✅ Updated version to v8.70\n4. ✅ Kept WhiteBalanceSearcher.run() mostly unchanged (already had correct initial value logic)\n\nKey changes in the algorithm:\n- Removed the 3-stage system (coarse/medium/fine)\n- Dynamic step size based on delta\n- Oscillation detection only at step=1\n- Global best tracking (no reset when entering different stages)\n\nNow let me report to the boss what was done.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板，v8.70 完成。\n\n**改动：**\n1. `whitebalance.py` — 重写 `IterativeWB` 类\n   - 动态步长：delta>10→±5，1<delta≤10→±2，delta≤1→±1\n   - 无步数限制\n   - step=1时，连续3次无改善（delta不下降）→ 回滚最佳值并停止\n   - 移除固定阶段（coarse/medium/fine）\n   - 移除精调20步上限\n\n2. `constants.py` — 版本 v8.69 → v8.70\n\n3. 备份：`backup_20260708_wb_redesign/whitebalance.py.bak`\n\n**初始值逻辑**：已确认原代码正确——auto模式→50/50，manual/locked→从当前值开始。\n\n**修复的核心问题**：\n- 原算法 fine 阶段 R/B 独立调整导致 B 永远不被选中\n- 现算法 step=1 时仍独立调整 R/B，但通过震荡检测（3次无改善）强制停止并回滚\n- 步长动态变化，delta 大时大步进，delta 小时小步进精调\n\n重启服务可测试。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":537,"cacheRead":98038,"cacheWrite":192,"totalTokens":98773,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783479224158,"responseId":"msg_c15c7f1d-bf30-4080-8276-f34c6b0ec855"}}
