{"type":"message","id":"57fcc126","parentId":"d58863e6","timestamp":"2026-07-08T02:56:12.983Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_219rq2h1lj0poztzlpm8tava","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"AstroHub v8.70 - 白平衡模块\n\n模块功能：\n- IterativeWB: 动态步长算法（delta>10→5步, 1-10→2步, <1→1步）\n- WhiteBalanceSearcher: 执行层（截图、设置参数、验证、SSE事件）\n\nv8.70 变更：\n- 移除固定阶段（coarse/medium/fine），改为动态步长\n- 移除固定步数限制，改为震荡3次停止\n- 步长：delta>10→5, 1<delta<=10→2, delta<=1→1\n- 震荡检测：step=1时，连续3次无改善→回滚最佳值并停止\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nimport asyncio\nfrom .region_base import _rgb_stats, calc_stable_delay\n\n\n# ==================================================================================================\n# 算法层：纯迭代搜索\n\n[330 more lines in file. Use offset=21 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783479372983}}
