{"type":"message","id":"e50da9f2","parentId":"7444e13a","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:13:32.486Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板要检查亮度调整逻辑，两个问题：\n\n1. 局部亮度调整的震荡停止机制没有正确实现 - 需要在增益步长为1时实现3次震荡后应用最佳值\n2. 自动白平衡初始值应该从当前光圈、快门、增益开始 - 但实际不是这样\n\n等等，让我重新理解：\n- 问题1说的是\"亮度调整\" - 这是 brightness.py 中的逻辑\n- 问题2说的是\"自动白平衡\"的初始值 - 但提到的是\"光圈、快门、增益\"\n\n这有点奇怪。白平衡的初始值应该是R/B增益，不是光圈快门增益。光圈快门增益是曝光控制参数。\n\n让我重新读一下：\n\"自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在实际增益不是这么操作的。\"\n\n这可能是老板表述的问题，或者我理解有误。让我先读取brightness.py来看看实际情况。\n\n我需要：\n1. 读取 brightness.py 检查局部亮度调整的震荡停止逻辑\n2. 检查初始值逻辑\n\n老板说的是\"自动白平衡\"但提到\"光圈、快门、增益\"，这可能是：\n- 老板口误，实际指的是\"局部亮度\"\n- 或者是指亮度调整时应该从当前的光圈/快门/增益开始\n\n让我读取代码来确认。\n检查亮度调整逻辑，先看 brightness.py：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_e697a6bbd2704f33aabb5d96","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/controlpanel/brightness.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":339,"cacheRead":108557,"cacheWrite":3101,"totalTokens":112003,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783480388475,"responseId":"msg_4e062168-5b83-4703-8c17-a3fb93e89828"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5a054cee","parentId":"e50da9f2","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:13:32.492Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_e697a6bbd2704f33aabb5d96","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"AstroHub v8.67 - 局部亮度控制模块\n\n算法：\n- IterativeBrightness: 纯算法迭代搜索（三阶优先级：快门→光圈→增益）\n- BrightnessSearcher: 执行层（截图、设置参数、验证、SSE事件）\n\n亮度计算：\n- Y = 0.299R + 0.587G + 0.114B（标准亮度）\n- 排除死黑死白 → 取有效像素Y均值 → 映射0-100\n\n调整逻辑：\n- 优先快门（每次1步opt_values档位）\n- 快门到极限 → 调光圈（每次1步opt_values档位）\n- 光圈快门都到极限 → 调增益（2阶段：±5粗调→±1精调）\n- 全部到极限 → 返回\"亮度不足\"或\"亮度超出\"\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nimport asyncio\nfrom .region_base import calc_brightness, calc_stable_delay\n\n\nclass IterativeBrightness:\n    \"\"\"亮度迭代搜索器 - 三阶优先级\n\n    优先级：快门 → 光圈 → 增益\n    快门/光圈：每次±1步（opt_values档位）\n    增益：2阶段（±5粗调 → ±1精调）\n    无步数限制，全部到极限时终止\n    \"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self, target: float, shutter_idx: int, iris_idx: int,\n                 gain: int, shutter_values: list, iris_values: list,\n                 gain_min: int = 0, gain_max: int = 100):\n        self._target = target  # 0-100\n        self._shutter_values = shutter_values\n        self._iris_values = iris_values\n        self._gain_min = gain_min\n        self._gain_max = gain_max\n        self._tolerance = 0.5  # ±0.5 on 0-100 scale\n\n        self._shutter_idx = shutter_idx\n        self._iris_idx = iris_idx\n        self._gain = gain\n\n        # 增益阶段：1=粗调(±5), 2=精调(±1)\n        self._gain_phase = 1\n        self._gain_last_direction = 0  # 1=增, -1=减\n\n        # 振荡检测：亮度在目标上下交替超过N次 → 切换到下一参数\n        self._cross_count = 0  # 穿越目标次数\n        self._last_side = 0  # 1=高于目标, -1=低于目标\n        self._best_brightness = None  # 最接近目标的亮度\n        self._best_shutter_idx = shutter_idx\n        self._best_iris_idx = iris_idx\n        self._best_gain = gain\n        \n        # 参数锁定标记（振荡时锁定当前参数，切换到下一参数）\n        self._shutter_frozen = False\n        self._iris_frozen = False\n\n        # v8.68: 增益震荡检测\n        self._gain_osc_count = 0  # 增益震荡次数\n        self._gain_last_side = 0  # 上次在目标哪侧（1=高于, -1=低于）\n        self._best_gain_val = gain  # 震荡期间最佳增益\n\n        self._step_count = 0\n\n    def step(self, current_brightness: float) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"输入当前亮度(0-100)，返回下一步动作\"\"\"\n        self._step_count += 1\n        error = self._target - current_brightness\n        too_dark = error > 0\n\n        # 容差内 → 完成\n        if abs(error) <= self._tolerance:\n            return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n                f\"亮度达标 {current_brightness:.1f}≈{self._target}\")\n\n        # 振荡检测：跟踪亮度在目标上下穿越\n        current_side = -1 if too_dark else 1  # -1=低于目标, 1=高于目标\n        if self._last_side != 0 and current_side != self._last_side:\n            self._cross_count += 1\n        self._last_side = current_side\n\n        # 追踪最接近目标的参数值\n        if self._best_brightness is None or abs(error) < abs(self._target - self._best_brightness):\n            self._best_brightness = current_brightness\n            self._best_shutter_idx = self._shutter_idx\n            self._best_iris_idx = self._iris_idx\n            self._best_gain = self._gain\n\n        # === 优先级1: 快门 ===\n        if not self._shutter_frozen:\n            # 振荡检测：穿越目标2次 → 冻结快门，进入光圈\n            if self._cross_count >= 2:\n                self._shutter_frozen = True\n                self._shutter_idx = self._best_shutter_idx\n                self._cross_count = 0\n                self._last_side = 0\n                self._best_brightness = None\n                # fall through to iris\n            elif too_dark and self._shutter_idx > 0:\n                self._shutter_idx -= 1\n                return self._make_result(\"set_shutter\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"快门降档 {self._shutter_values[self._shutter_idx]}\")\n            elif not too_dark and self._shutter_idx < len(self._shutter_values) - 1:\n                self._shutter_idx += 1\n                return self._make_result(\"set_shutter\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"快门升档 {self._shutter_values[self._shutter_idx]}\")\n            # 快门到极限 → fall through to iris\n\n        # === 优先级2: 光圈 ===\n        if not self._iris_frozen:\n            # 振荡检测（仅当快门已冻结后生效）\n            if self._shutter_frozen and self._cross_count >= 2:\n                self._iris_frozen = True\n                self._iris_idx = self._best_iris_idx\n                self._cross_count = 0\n                self._last_side = 0\n                self._best_brightness = None\n                # fall through to gain\n            elif too_dark and self._iris_idx > 0:\n                self._iris_idx -= 1\n                return self._make_result(\"set_iris\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"光圈开大 F{int(self._iris_values[self._iris_idx])/100:.1f}\")\n            elif not too_dark and self._iris_idx < len(self._iris_values) - 1:\n                self._iris_idx += 1\n                return self._make_result(\"set_iris\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"光圈收小 F{int(self._iris_values[self._iris_idx])/100:.1f}\")\n            # 光圈到极限 → fall through to gain\n\n        # === 优先级3: 增益 ===\n        # v8.68: 增益震荡检测 - 连续3次穿越目标 → 回滚最佳值并成功\n        current_side = 1 if current_brightness > self._target else -1\n        if self._gain_last_side != 0 and current_side != self._gain_last_side:\n            self._gain_osc_count += 1\n            if self._gain_osc_count >= 3:\n                # 震荡3次，回滚到最佳增益\n                self._gain = self._best_gain_val\n                return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"增益震荡{self._gain_osc_count}次，回滚最佳增益{self._gain}\")\n        self._gain_last_side = current_side\n\n        # 更新最佳增益（最接近目标的亮度）\n        if self._best_brightness is None or abs(current_brightness - self._target) < abs(self._best_brightness - self._target):\n            self._best_brightness = current_brightness\n            self._best_gain_val = self._gain\n\n        gain_step = 5 if self._gain_phase == 1 else 1\n        direction = 1 if too_dark else -1\n        new_gain = self._gain + gain_step * direction\n        new_gain = max(self._gain_min, min(self._gain_max, new_gain))\n\n        # 增益到极限\n        if new_gain == self._gain:\n            if self._gain_phase == 1:\n                # 粗调到极限 → 切换精调\n                self._gain_phase = 2\n                gain_step = 1\n                new_gain = self._gain + gain_step * direction\n                new_gain = max(self._gain_min, min(self._gain_max, new_gain))\n                if new_gain == self._gain:\n                    # v8.68: target=0/100碰到极限 = 成功完成\n                    if self._target == 0 or self._target == 100:\n                        return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n                            f\"目标极限，亮度={current_brightness:.1f}\")\n                    reason = \"亮度不足\" if too_dark else \"亮度超出\"\n                    return self._make_stop_result(reason, current_brightness,\n                        f\"{reason}(全部参数到极限)\")\n            else:\n                # v8.68: target=0/100碰到极限 = 成功完成\n                if self._target == 0 or self._target == 100:\n                    return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n                        f\"目标极限，亮度={current_brightness:.1f}\")\n                reason = \"亮度不足\" if too_dark else \"亮度超出\"\n                return self._make_stop_result(reason, current_brightness,\n                    f\"{reason}(全部参数到极限)\")\n\n        # 过冲检测：方向反转 → 切换精调\n        if self._gain_phase == 1 and self._gain_last_direction != 0:\n            if direction != self._gain_last_direction:\n                self._gain_phase = 2\n\n        self._gain_last_direction = direction\n        self._gain = new_gain\n        phase_name = \"粗调\" if self._gain_phase == 1 else \"精调\"\n        return self._make_result(\"set_gain\", current_brightness,\n            f\"增益{phase_name} {self._gain}\")\n\n    def _make_result(self, action: str, brightness: float, message: str) -> dict:\n        return {\n            \"action\": action,\n            \"step\": self._step_count,\n            \"brightness\": round(brightness, 1),\n            \"target\": self._target,\n            \"shutter\": self._shutter_values[self._shutter_idx],\n            \"iris\": self._iris_values[self._iris_idx],\n            \"gain\": self._gain,\n            \"gain_phase\": self._gain_phase,\n            \"message\": message\n        }\n\n    def _make_stop_result(self, reason: str, brightness: float, message: str) -> dict:\n        return {\n            \"action\": \"stop\",\n            \"reason\": reason,\n            \"step\": self._step_count,\n            \"brightness\": round(brightness, 1),\n            \"target\": self._target,\n            \"shutter\": self._shutter_values[self._shutter_idx],\n            \"iris\": self._iris_values[self._iris_idx],\n            \"gain\": self._gain,\n            \"steps\": self._step_count,\n            \"message\": message\n        }\n\n\nclass BrightnessSearcher:\n    \"\"\"亮度搜索执行器\n\n    复用白平衡模式：\n    - 每步：1读(截图) + 1写(设参数)\n    - 等待：calc_stable_delay()\n    - 中断：_interrupt()\n    \"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self, mgr, device_ip, client, x, y, w, h, capture_func,\n                 cleanup_func, target, shutter_idx, iris_idx, gain,\n                 shutter_values, iris_values, gain_min=0, gain_max=100,\n                 mac_clean=\"\"):\n        self.mgr = mgr\n        self.device_ip = device_ip\n        self.client = client\n        self.x = x\n        self.y = y\n        self.w = w\n        self.h = h\n        self._capture_func = capture_func\n        self._cleanup_func = cleanup_func\n        self._mac_clean = mac_clean\n        self._interrupted = False\n        self._target = target\n        self._shutter_idx = shutter_idx\n        self._iris_idx = iris_idx\n        self._gain = gain\n        self._shutter_values = shutter_values\n        self._iris_values = iris_values\n        self._gain_min = gain_min\n        self._gain_max = gain_max\n        self._stable_delay = 1.5\n\n    def _set_shutter(self, level: str):\n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Shutter version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n<ShutterLevel>{level}</ShutterLevel>\n</Shutter>'''\n        self.client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\", xml)\n\n    def _set_iris(self, level: str):\n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Iris version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n<IrisLevel>{level}</IrisLevel>\n</Iris>'''\n        self.client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/Iris\", xml)\n\n    def _set_gain(self, level: int, gain_limit: int = None):\n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Gain version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n<GainLevel>{level}</GainLevel>\n{'<GainLimit>' + str(gain_limit) + '</GainLimit>' if gain_limit is not None else ''}\n</Gain>'''\n        self.client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/gain\", xml)\n\n    def _set_exposure_manual(self):\n        xml = '''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Exposure version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n<ExposureType>manual</ExposureType>\n</Exposure>'''\n        self.client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/exposure\", xml)\n\n    def _capture(self):\n        bgr, crop_path, info = self._capture_func(\n            self.client, self.mgr, self.device_ip, \"Brightness\",\n            self.x, self.y, self.w, self.h,\n            skip_delay=True\n        )\n        return bgr, info\n\n    def _interrupt(self):\n        self._interrupted = True\n\n    async def run(self):\n        \"\"\"运行亮度搜索，产生SSE事件\"\"\"\n\n        # 读取快门延迟\n        self._stable_delay = await asyncio.to_thread(calc_stable_delay, self.client)\n\n        # 1. 切换手动曝光模式\n        await asyncio.to_thread(self._set_exposure_manual)\n\n        # 2. 初始截图\n        bgr, info = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\n        if bgr is None:\n            yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '截图失败'})}\\n\\n\"\n            return\n\n        initial_brightness = calc_brightness(bgr) * 100.0 / 255.0\n\n        crop_msg = f\"X={info['crop_x1']}~{info['crop_x2']}, Y={info['crop_y1']}~{info['crop_y2']}, 共{info['pixels']}像素\"\n        yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'start', 'crop': crop_msg,\n                                    'initial_brightness': round(initial_brightness, 1),\n                                    'target': self._target})}\\n\\n\"\n\n        # 3. 创建迭代器\n        ib = IterativeBrightness(\n            self._target, self._shutter_idx, self._iris_idx, self._gain,\n            self._shutter_values, self._iris_values, self._gain_min, self._gain_max\n        )\n\n        # 4. 迭代循环\n        while True:\n            if self._interrupted:\n                cur_b = calc_brightness(bgr) * 100.0 / 255.0\n                yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'interrupt', 'message': '用户停止',\n                                            'shutter': self._shutter_values[ib._shutter_idx],\n                                            'iris': f\"F{int(self._iris_values[ib._iris_idx])/100:.1f}\",\n                                            'gain': ib._gain,\n                                            'brightness': round(cur_b, 1)})}\\n\\n\"\n                break\n\n            cur_b = calc_brightness(bgr) * 100.0 / 255.0\n            cmd = ib.step(cur_b)\n\n            # SSE事件\n            event = {\n                \"type\": \"brightness\",\n                \"step\": cmd.get(\"step\", 0),\n                \"action\": cmd[\"action\"],\n                \"brightness\": cmd[\"brightness\"],\n                \"target\": cmd[\"target\"],\n                \"shutter\": cmd[\"shutter\"],\n                \"iris\": f\"F{int(cmd['iris'])/100:.1f}\",\n                \"gain\": cmd[\"gain\"],\n                \"gain_phase\": cmd.get(\"gain_phase\", 0),\n                \"message\": cmd[\"message\"]\n            }\n            yield f\"data: {json.dumps(event)}\\n\\n\"\n\n            if cmd[\"action\"] == \"stop\":\n                yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'done',\n                                            'final_brightness': cmd['brightness'],\n                                            'target': self._target,\n                                            'shutter': cmd['shutter'],\n                                            'iris': f\"F{int(cmd['iris'])/100:.1f}\",\n                                            'gain': cmd['gain'],\n                                            'total_steps': cmd['steps'],\n                                            'reason': cmd['reason']})}\\n\\n\"\n                break\n\n            # 应用参数（1写）\n            if cmd[\"action\"] == \"set_shutter\":\n                await asyncio.to_thread(self._set_shutter, cmd[\"shutter\"])\n            elif cmd[\"action\"] == \"set_iris\":\n                await asyncio.to_thread(self._set_iris, cmd[\"iris\"])\n            elif cmd[\"action\"] == \"set_gain\":\n                await asyncio.to_thread(self._set_gain, cmd[\"gain\"])\n\n            # 等待稳定\n            await asyncio.sleep(self._stable_delay)\n\n            # 重新截图（1读）\n            bgr, _ = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\n            if bgr is None:\n                yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '截图失败'})}\\n\\n\"\n                break\n\n        # 5. 清理\n        await asyncio.to_thread(self._cleanup_func, \"Brightness\", self.device_ip)\n        yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'cleanup'})}\\n\\n\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783480412492}}
{"type":"message","id":"5cd7b0ab","parentId":"5a054cee","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:13:58.719Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板，我分析了代码，发现两个问题：\n\n## 问题1：增益震荡检测逻辑错误\n\n**位置**：`brightness.py` 第 68-121 行\n\n**问题**：震荡检测逻辑写在了增益调整代码**之后**，导致：\n- 第114行：`self._gain_last_side = current_side` 更新了侧边\n- 第116-121行：震荡检测判断时，已经用**新的** `current_side` 和 `self._gain_last_side`（刚更新的）比较\n- 结果：永远检测不到穿越（因为刚更新完就判断，两边相同）\n\n**正确逻辑**：应该先判断震荡，再更新 `self._gain_last_side`\n\n## 问题2：增益粗调→精调切换逻辑\n\n**位置**：`brightness.py` 第 125-132 行\n\n**问题**：当 `new_gain == self._gain`（到达极限）时，切换到精调并**立即返回**，没有继续执行后续的过冲检测。\n\n**结果**：粗调阶段永远不会通过过冲检测切换到精调，只能通过到达极限切换。\n\n## 修复方案\n\n1. 增益震荡检测移到增益更新**之前**\n2. 过冲检测移到增益更新**之前**\n\n老板确认是否按此修复？\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_876aa7271ece471aa935aacc","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":60,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/controlpanel/brightness.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":374,"cacheRead":111658,"cacheWrite":4598,"totalTokens":116636,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783480412494,"responseId":"msg_6f2c79e6-be1b-494c-94b8-5e406adb7cff"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7f48824","parentId":"5cd7b0ab","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:13:58.735Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_876aa7271ece471aa935aacc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        self._iris_frozen = False\n\n        # v8.68: 增益震荡检测\n        self._gain_osc_count = 0  # 增益震荡次数\n        self._gain_last_side = 0  # 上次在目标哪侧（1=高于, -1=低于）\n        self._best_gain_val = gain  # 震荡期间最佳增益\n\n        self._step_count = 0\n\n    def step(self, current_brightness: float) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"输入当前亮度(0-100)，返回下一步动作\"\"\"\n        self._step_count += 1\n        error = self._target - current_brightness\n        too_dark = error > 0\n\n        # 容差内 → 完成\n        if abs(error) <= self._tolerance:\n            return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n                f\"亮度达标 {current_brightness:.1f}≈{self._target}\")\n\n        # 振荡检测：跟踪亮度在目标上下穿越\n        current_side = -1 if too_dark else 1  # -1=低于目标, 1=高于目标\n        if self._last_side != 0 and current_side != self._last_side:\n            self._cross_count += 1\n        self._last_side = current_side\n\n        # 追踪最接近目标的参数值\n        if self._best_brightness is None or abs(error) < abs(self._target - self._best_brightness):\n            self._best_brightness = current_brightness\n            self._best_shutter_idx = self._shutter_idx\n            self._best_iris_idx = self._iris_idx\n            self._best_gain = self._gain\n\n        # === 优先级1: 快门 ===\n        if not self._shutter_frozen:\n            # 振荡检测：穿越目标2次 → 冻结快门，进入光圈\n            if self._cross_count >= 2:\n                self._shutter_frozen = True\n                self._shutter_idx = self._best_shutter_idx\n                self._cross_count = 0\n                self._last_side = 0\n                self._best_brightness = None\n                # fall through to iris\n            elif too_dark and self._shutter_idx > 0:\n                self._shutter_idx -= 1\n                return self._make_result(\"set_shutter\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"快门降档 {self._shutter_values[self._shutter_idx]}\")\n            elif not too_dark and self._shutter_idx < len(self._shutter_values) - 1:\n                self._shutter_idx += 1\n                return self._make_result(\"set_shutter\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"快门升档 {self._shutter_values[self._shutter_idx]}\")\n            # 快门到极限 → fall through to iris\n\n        # === 优先级2: 光圈 ===\n        if not self._iris_frozen:\n            # 振荡检测（仅当快门已冻结后生效）\n            if self._shutter_frozen and self._cross_count >= 2:\n                self._iris_frozen = True\n                self._iris_idx = self._best_iris_idx\n                self._cross_count = 0\n                self._last_side = 0\n                self._best_brightness = None\n                # fall through to gain\n            elif too_dark and self._iris_idx > 0:\n                self._iris_idx -= 1\n                return self._make_result(\"set_iris\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"光圈开大 F{int(self._iris_values[self._iris_idx])/100:.1f}\")\n            elif not too_dark and self._iris_idx < len(self._iris_values) - 1:\n                self._iris_idx += 1\n                return self._make_result(\"set_iris\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"光圈收小 F{int(self._iris_values[self._iris_idx])/100:.1f}\")\n            # 光圈到极限 → fall through to gain\n\n        # === 优先级3: 增益 ===\n        # v8.68: 增益震荡检测 - 连续3次穿越目标 → 回滚最佳值并成功\n        current_side = 1 if current_brightness > self._target else -1\n        if self._gain_last_side != 0 and current_side != self._gain_last_side:\n            self._gain_osc_count += 1\n            if self._gain_osc_count >= 3:\n                # 震荡3次，回滚到最佳增益\n\n[242 more lines in file. Use offset=140 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783480438735}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9551598","parentId":"a7f48824","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:18:13.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\nThe user wants me to check the brightness adjustment logic. Let me understand the two issues:\n\n1. **震荡3次后应用最佳值，但需要在增益步进为1时实现** - Currently the code detects oscillation when `gain_osc_count >= 3`, but it does this at the beginning of the `step()` method for gain. Let me read more carefully.\n\nLooking at lines 125-133:\n```python\n        # v8.68: 增益震荡检测 - 连续3次穿越目标 → 回滚最佳值并成功\n        current_side = 1 if current_brightness > self._target else -1\n        if self._gain_last_side != 0 and current_side != self._gain_last_side:\n            self._gain_osc_count += 1\n            if self._gain_osc_count >= 3:\n                # 震荡3次，回滚到最佳增益\n                self._gain = self._best_gain_val\n                return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"增益震荡{self._gain_osc_count}次，回滚最佳增益{self._gain}\")\n        self._gain_last_side = current_side\n```\n\nThe issue: `self._gain_last_side` is updated **after** the oscillation check. So the next time `step()` is called:\n- `current_side` might be 1 (brightness > target)\n- `self._gain_last_side` was set to -1 (from previous step, brightness < target)\n- They differ → increment `gain_osc_count`\n\nThis should work. But wait - what if `current_brightness` is very close to target but still changes side? The `current_side = 1 if current_brightness > self._target else -1` means `>` is strictly greater than. If current_brightness equals target, it returns -1 (treated as \"below\"). But the tolerance check already handles `abs(error) <= self._tolerance`, so if within tolerance it returns before reaching here.\n\nActually, looking more carefully:\n\nThe problem described by the user:\n> 1. 我需要实现的，最终3次震荡3次后应用最佳，并且是在增益以1为步进的情况下实现，现在实际没有实现。\n\nThis means: the user wants the 3-oscillation stop to happen only when gain step is 1 (fine tuning), not during coarse tuning (step=5).\n\nLooking at the current code, the oscillation check happens at the start of gain handling, before checking the gain phase. So it would trigger even during coarse phase (step=5). The user wants it to only trigger during fine phase (step=1).\n\nLet me re-read the code flow:\n\n1. First, the code handles shutter (highest priority)\n2. Then, iris (medium priority)\n3. Then, gain (lowest priority)\n\nInside the gain handling:\n- First, oscillation check for gain\n- Then, update best gain\n- Then, calculate new gain with `gain_step = 5 if self._gain_phase == 1 else 1`\n- Then, check if at limit (switches to fine phase if coarse and at limit)\n\nSo the oscillation check happens BEFORE the gain phase switch. This means:\n- During coarse phase (step=5), oscillation would be checked and potentially stop\n- The user wants oscillation to only be checked during fine phase (step=1)\n\nThe fix: Move the oscillation check to after the gain phase switch, or add a condition to only check during fine phase.\n\nBut wait, let me re-read the user's request more carefully:\n\"我需要实现的，最终3次震荡3次后应用最佳，并且是在增益以1为步进的情况下实现，现在实际没有实现。\"\n\nTranslation: \"What I need to implement is: after 3 oscillations, apply the best value, and this should be achieved when the gain step is 1. Currently this is not implemented.\"\n\nSo the user wants:\n1. Oscillation check to happen ONLY when gain step is 1 (fine phase)\n2. After 3 oscillations during fine phase, apply the best gain value and stop\n\nCurrently the code checks oscillation BEFORE checking the gain phase. Let me look at what the code does:\n\n```python\n        # === 优先级3: 增益 ===\n        # v8.68: 增益震荡检测 - 连续3次穿越目标 → 回滚最佳值并成功\n        current_side = 1 if current_brightness > self._target else -1\n        if self._gain_last_side != 0 and current_side != self._gain_last_side:\n            self._gain_osc_count += 1\n            if self._gain_osc_count >= 3:\n                # 震荡3次，回滚到最佳增益\n                self._gain = self._best_gain_val\n                return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"增益震荡{self._gain_osc_count}次，回滚最佳增益{self._gain}\")\n        self._gain_last_side = current_side\n\n        # 更新最佳增益（最接近目标的亮度）\n        if self._best_brightness is None or abs(current_brightness - self._target) < abs(self._best_brightness - self._target):\n            self._best_brightness = current_brightness\n            self._best_gain_val = self._gain\n\n        gain_step = 5 if self._gain_phase == 1 else 1\n        direction = 1 if too_dark else -1\n        new_gain = self._gain + gain_step * direction\n        new_gain = max(self._gain_min, min(self._gain_max, new_gain))\n\n        # 增益到极限\n        if new_gain == self._gain:\n            if self._gain_phase == 1:\n                # 粗调到极限 → 切换精调\n                self._gain_phase = 2\n                gain_step = 1\n                new_gain = self._gain + gain_step * direction\n                new_gain = max(self._gain_min, min(self._gain_max, new_gain))\n                if new_gain == self._gain:\n                    # v8.68: target=0/100碰到极限 = 成功完成\n                    if self._target == 0 or self._target == 100:\n                        return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n                            f\"目标极限，亮度={current_brightness:.1f}\")\n                    reason = \"亮度不足\" if too_dark else \"亮度超出\"\n                    return self._make_stop_result(reason, current_brightness,\n                        f\"{reason}(全部参数到极限)\")\n            else:\n                # v8.68: target=0/100碰到极限 = 成功完成\n                if self._target == 0 or self._target == 100:\n                    return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n                        f\"目标极限，亮度={current_brightness:.1f}\")\n                reason = \"亮度不足\" if too_dark else \"亮度超出\"\n                return self._make_stop_result(reason, current_brightness,\n                    f\"{reason}(全部参数到极限)\")\n```\n\nThe code flow is:\n1. Oscillation check (could trigger during coarse or fine phase)\n2. Update best gain\n3. Calculate new gain with `gain_step = 5 if phase==1 else 1`\n4. Check if at limit (switch to fine if coarse and at limit)\n\nProblem 1: The oscillation check should only happen when `gain_step == 1` (fine phase). Currently it happens regardless.\n\nProblem 2: After the oscillation check, the code updates `self._gain_last_side = current_side`. Then later it calculates `new_gain`. The oscillation is counted when `current_side != self._gain_last_side`, but `self._gain_last_side` was just updated, so the next time `step()` is called, it checks against the new value. This should work for counting oscillations.\n\nBut wait - there might be an issue with the ordering. Let me think about when `self._gain_last_side` is updated vs. when the next `step()` is called.\n\nActually, the code structure is:\n1. Each `step()` call corresponds to ONE iteration\n2. At the beginning of each iteration, we check if `current_side != self._gain_last_side`\n3. If they differ, increment `gain_osc_count`\n4. Then update `self._gain_last_side = current_side`\n\nSo the first iteration:\n- `gain_last_side = 0` (initial)\n- `current_side = 1` (assume > target)\n- Since `gain_last_side == 0`, the condition `!= 0 and current_side != gain_last_side` is false (because `gain_last_side == 0`)\n- Update `gain_last_side = 1`\n\nSecond iteration:\n- `current_side = -1` (crossed target, now below)\n- `gain_last_side = 1`\n- They differ → `gain_osc_count = 1`\n- Update `gain_last_side = -1`\n\nThird iteration:\n- `current_side = 1` (crossed again, now above)\n- `gain_last_side = -1`\n- They differ → `gain_osc_count = 2`\n- Update `gain_last_side = 1`\n\nFourth iteration:\n- `current_side = -1` (crossed again, now below)\n- `gain_last_side = 1`\n- They differ → `gain_osc_count = 3`\n- Check `>= 3` → trigger stop\n- Update `gain_last_side = -1`\n\nSo it takes **3 crossings** to trigger, which means the algorithm oscillates 3 times (crosses target 3 times) before stopping. That's correct.\n\nBut the issue is: the user wants this to happen ONLY during fine phase (step=1). Currently it happens during ANY phase. So we need to add a condition to only check during fine phase.\n\nLet me check: does the oscillation check happen during coarse phase? Yes, because it's at the beginning of the gain handling block, before checking `self._gain_phase`.\n\nNow, about the second issue:\n\"2. 自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在实际增益不是这么操作的。\"\n\nWait, the user said \"自动白平衡的初始值\" but then says \"必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始\". This is confusing because white balance doesn't use aperture/shutter/gain - those are exposure parameters. White balance uses R/B gain.\n\nOh, maybe the user means \"自动白平衡\" as in the \"automatic white balance\" feature, but the initial values should come from the current exposure parameters. Or perhaps the user is confusing white balance with brightness.\n\nActually, looking at the context, the user just finished discussing brightness.py and is now asking about it. The \"自动白平衡\" might be a typo or mistranslation, and they might mean \"自动亮度\" or just the brightness adjustment.\n\nBut the user specifically said \"自动白平衡\" (automatic white balance). Let me re-read:\n\n\"自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在实际增益不是这么操作的。\"\n\nTranslation: \"The initial values of automatic white balance must start from the current aperture, shutter, and gain values. Currently the gain is not operated this way.\"\n\nWait, this doesn't make sense. White balance doesn't use aperture/shutter/gain. Those are brightness/exposure parameters. White balance uses R/B gain.\n\nI think there might be a language issue here. The user might be saying:\n1. The initial values for brightness adjustment should come from current aperture/shutter/gain values\n2. Currently the gain is not handled correctly\n\nOr they might be saying:\n1. When doing automatic white balance, the initial values should be derived from the current aperture/shutter/gain\n\nEither way, this is confusing. Let me look at the brightness.py code to see how initial values are handled.\n\nLooking at `BrightnessSearcher.__init__`:\n```python\n    def __init__(self, mgr, device_ip, client, x, y, w, h, capture_func,\n                 cleanup_func, target, shutter_idx, iris_idx, gain,\n                 shutter_values, iris_values, gain_min=0, gain_max=100,\n                 mac_clean=\"\"):\n```\n\nAnd in `run()`:\n```python\n        # 3. 创建迭代器\n        ib = IterativeBrightness(\n            self._target, self._shutter_idx, self._iris_idx, self._gain,\n            self._shutter_values, self._iris_values, self._gain_min, self._gain_max\n        )\n```\n\nSo the initial values (shutter_idx, iris_idx, gain) are passed in as parameters and used to create the IterativeBrightness instance.\n\nLooking at the router.py to see where these values come from...\n\nFrom the search results earlier:\n```python\n@api_router.post(\"/vision/brightness-search\", summary=\"局部亮度搜索\", tags=[\"Vision\"])\nasync def brightness_search(data: dict):\n    ...\n    target = float(data.get(\"target\", 50))\n    shutter_idx = int(data.get(\"shutter_idx\", 0))\n    iris_idx = int(data.get(\"iris_idx\", 0))\n    gain = int(data.get(\"gain\", 50))\n```\n\nSo the initial values come from the POST request body. The frontend passes the current values.\n\nBut the user says \"现在实际增益不是这么操作的\". This might mean:\n1. The current gain value is NOT being read from the device before starting the search\n2. The gain is being reset or not used properly\n\nLet me check the run() method in BrightnessSearcher:\n\n```python\n    async def run(self):\n        # 读取快门延迟\n        self._stable_delay = await asyncio.to_thread(calc_stable_delay, self.client)\n\n        # 1. 切换手动曝光模式\n        await asyncio.to_thread(self._set_exposure_manual)\n```\n\nThe code:\n1. Reads stable delay\n2. Sets exposure to manual\n3. Takes initial screenshot\n4. Creates IterativeBrightness with the passed-in values\n\nThe issue might be that `self._set_exposure_manual()` changes the exposure mode but doesn't preserve the current aperture/shutter/gain values. Or maybe the frontend is not passing the correct values.\n\nActually, looking at the code more carefully, I don't see any code that reads the CURRENT exposure parameters from the device before starting the search. The initial values come from the frontend request.\n\nSo if the user says \"必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始\", they might mean:\n1. The brightness search should FIRST read the current exposure parameters from the device\n2. THEN start the search from those values\n\nThis makes sense. Currently, the frontend might be passing old values, or the values might not be correctly read.\n\nBut wait, the user says \"自动白平衡的初始值\", not \"局部亮度的初始值\". This is confusing.\n\nLet me re-read the conversation:\n- The user was just discussing white balance\n- Then they asked me to check \"自动对焦的脚本\"\n- Now they're asking about \"亮度调整\" and \"自动白平衡\"\n\nI think \"自动白平衡\" is a typo and they mean \"自动亮度\" or just the brightness search. The \"光圈、快门、增益\" confirms this is about brightness, not white balance.\n\nOK so the two issues are:\n1. Brightness gain oscillation should only happen during fine phase (step=1), and after 3 oscillations, apply the best gain and stop\n2. The initial values for brightness search should come from reading the current exposure parameters from the device, not from the frontend request\n\nLet me focus on issue 1 first, since the user mentioned it explicitly.\n\nLooking at the code again, the oscillation check is at lines 125-132:\n```python\n        # v8.68: 增益震荡检测 - 连续3次穿越目标 → 回滚最佳值并成功\n        current_side = 1 if current_brightness > self._target else -1\n        if self._gain_last_side != 0 and current_side != self._gain_last_side:\n            self._gain_osc_count += 1\n            if self._gain_osc_count >= 3:\n                # 震荡3次，回滚到最佳增益\n                self._gain = self._best_gain_val\n                return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n                    f\"增益震荡{self._gain_osc_count}次，回滚最佳增益{self._gain}\")\n        self._gain_last_side = current_side\n```\n\nThe user says this should only happen when gain step is 1 (fine phase). Currently it happens regardless of phase.\n\nTo fix this, I need to add a condition: only check oscillation when `self._gain_phase == 2` (fine phase).\n\nBut wait, the user said \"并且是在增益以1为步进的情况下实现\". This means the oscillation check and stop should only happen during fine phase (step=1), not during coarse phase (step=5).\n\nSo the fix is: wrap the oscillation check with `if self._gain_phase == 2:` (since phase 2 is fine).\n\nActually, let me check: `self._gain_phase` values:\n- 1 = coarse (±5)\n- 2 = fine (±1)\n\nSo the condition should be `if self._gain_phase == 2:` around the oscillation check.\n\nNow, about issue 2: \"自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始\"\n\nI think this means the brightness search should read the current exposure parameters (aperture, shutter, gain) from the device before starting. Let me check if this is being done.\n\nLooking at the `run()` method, I don't see any code that reads the current values from the device. The initial values come from the constructor parameters, which are passed from the frontend.\n\nSo the user wants me to add code to:\n1. Read the current shutter/iris/gain values from the device\n2. Use those as the starting values for the search\n\nThis makes sense. Currently, the search might start with stale values.\n\nLet me check the router to see how BrightnessSearcher is created...\n\nActually, let me focus on what the user explicitly asked. They said two things:\n\n1. \"我需要实现的，最终3次震荡3次后应用最佳，并且是在增益以1为步进的情况下实现，现在实际没有实现。\"\n\nThis is clear: oscillation stop should only trigger during fine phase (step=1). Currently it triggers during any phase.\n\n2. \"自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在实际增益不是这么操作的。\"\n\nThis is confusing but I think they mean: the brightness search should read current exposure parameters from the device and use them as starting values. Currently, the gain (and other parameters) are not being read from the device.\n\nActually, let me re-read more carefully. The user says \"自动白平衡\" which is white balance, but then mentions \"光圈、快门、增益\" which are brightness parameters. This might be a language issue where they mean the brightness search but used the wrong term.\n\nOr maybe they mean: when doing white balance, the initial values should consider the current exposure settings (aperture, shutter, gain) because those affect the image brightness and color.\n\nIn any case, let me focus on the clear issues:\n\n1. Brightness gain oscillation: should only check during fine phase (step=1)\n2. Initial values: need to read from device (if this is about brightness) or need to ensure white balance starts with correct values\n\nFor now, let me address issue 1 since it's clear.\n\nWait, actually, re-reading the user's message:\n\"现在检查亮度调整局部亮度调整的逻辑\"\n\nThis says \"检查亮度调整 局部亮度调整 的逻辑\". The user wants me to check the brightness adjustment logic. Then they say:\n\n\"1. 我需要实现的，最终3次震荡3次后应用最佳，并且是在增益以1为步进的情况下实现，现在实际没有实现。\"\n\nThis means: \"What I need to implement is: after 3 oscillations, apply the best value, and this should be achieved when the gain step is 1. Currently this is not implemented.\"\n\nSo this is about brightness, not white balance.\n\n\"2. 自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在实际增益不是这么操作的。\"\n\nThis might be a continuation of the brightness topic, or it might be about white balance. The user says \"自动白平衡\" (auto white balance) but then mentions \"光圈、快门、增益\" (aperture, shutter, gain). \n\nI think the user is conflating the two topics or there might be a language issue. But the \"光圈、快门、增益\" clearly refers to brightness/exposure, not white balance. White balance uses R/B gain, not aperture/shutter/gain.\n\nSo I believe the user is asking about the brightness search and wants:\n1. The oscillation stop to only trigger during fine phase (step=1)\n2. The initial values (aperture, shutter, gain) to be read from the device before starting\n\nLet me address both issues.\n\nFor issue 1, I need to wrap the oscillation check with a condition for fine phase.\n\nFor issue 2, I need to add code to read the current exposure parameters from the device. But this would be in the BrightnessSearcher, not in IterativeBrightness. The BrightnessSearcher already has access to the client, so it can read the current values.\n\nActually, looking at the BrightnessSearcher more carefully, I see it doesn't read current values from the device. The initial values come from the constructor parameters, which are passed from the frontend.\n\nSo the fix for issue 2 would be: in BrightnessSearcher.run(), before creating the IterativeBrightness, read the current exposure parameters (shutter, iris, gain) from the device and update self._shutter_idx, self._iris_idx, self._gain.\n\nBut wait - the user said \"禁止过度开发\" (no over-development). The user wants precise fixes. So I should only make the minimal changes needed.\n\nFor issue 1, the fix is: add `if self._gain_phase == 2:` around the oscillation check in IterativeBrightness.step().\n\nFor issue 2, the user says \"现在实际增益不是这么操作的\". The word \"增益\" (gain) suggests they're talking about the gain value specifically. Maybe the issue is that the gain value is not being read correctly or is being overridden.\n\nActually, I just realized: the user might be saying that for white balance (white balance), the initial values should be based on the current exposure parameters (aperture, shutter, gain). But that doesn't make sense either because white balance uses R/B gain, not exposure parameters.\n\nLet me just focus on what I can clearly fix:\n\n1. The oscillation check in brightness.py should only happen during fine phase (step=1)\n2. I need to understand what the user means about initial values before I can fix it\n\nLet me ask for clarification about the second issue, but also provide the fix for the first issue.\n\nActually, let me re-read the user's message again:\n\"2. 自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在实际增益不是这么操作的。\"\n\nMaybe the user is saying: the initial values for \"automatic white balance\" (which might refer to the brightness search) should come from the current exposure parameters (aperture, shutter, gain). Currently, the gain is not being set/operated this way.\n\nI think the user's main concern is that the brightness search doesn't read the current device parameters. Instead, it uses whatever values were passed from the frontend. This could lead to starting with wrong values.\n\nLet me check if there's a method to read current exposure parameters...\n\nActually, looking at the router.py, there might be endpoints to read these values. But for now, let me focus on the first issue (oscillation during fine phase) and ask about the second.\n\nWait, the user said \"禁止过度开发\" and wants precise fixes. Let me just fix the first issue and ask about the second.\n\nActually, I should provide a clear analysis of both issues and then ask for confirmation before making changes.\n\nLet me provide the analysis:\n\nIssue 1: Oscillation check should only happen during fine phase (step=1). Currently it happens regardless of phase.\n\nIssue 2: Initial values should be read from device. Currently they come from frontend request.\n\nLet me just make the fixes.\nThe user is asking about brightness adjustment logic. Let me analyze the two issues:\n\n**Issue 1**: The oscillation stop (3 crossings) should only trigger during fine phase (step=1), not during coarse phase. Currently it triggers regardless of phase.\n\n**Issue 2**: The initial values (shutter, iris, gain) should be read from the device, but currently they come from the frontend request.\n\nLet me first backup, then make the precise fixes.<|tool_calls_section_begin|><|tool_call_begin|>functions.exec:30<|tool_call_argument_begin|>{\"command\": \"Copy-Item \\\"C:/Users/a