{"type":"message","id":"4f4a116c","parentId":"c41f9ad9","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:28:11.285Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板要求修复亮度调整的两个问题，然后报告。让我先明确问题：\n\n**问题1**：增益震荡3次后应用最佳值 — 但需要在增益步长为1（精调阶段）时检测，现在在粗调阶段就检测了。\n\n**问题2**：局部亮度调整的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在增益不是这样操作的。\n\n等等，问题2说的是\"自动白平衡\"还是\"局部亮度\"？让我重新看用户的原话：\n\n> 1. 我需要实现的，最终3次震荡3次后应用最佳，并且是在增益以1为步进的情况下实现，现在实际没有实现。\n> 2. 自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在实际增益不是这么操作的。\n\n问题2说的是\"自动白平衡\" — 但这和白平衡有什么关系？白平衡是调R/B增益，和光圈快门增益是曝光控制。\n\n哦等等，我想起来了。用户说的\"自动白平衡\"可能是指亮度搜索。因为在HEARTBEAT.md中，局部亮度控制确实是从白平衡模块衍生出来的。\n\n但更可能的是，用户混淆了术语。让我重新理解：\n\n\"自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在实际增益不是这么操作的。\"\n\n这里的\"初始值\"可能指的是白平衡搜索时，设备的曝光参数（光圈、快门、增益）应该固定，或者白平衡搜索应该在当前曝光参数基础上进行。\n\n不对，让我再想想。用户说的是\"自动白平衡\" — 但白平衡是调R/B增益，不是光圈快门增益。\n\n等等！我突然明白了。用户可能在说\"自动曝光\"而不是\"自动白平衡\"。因为光圈、快门、增益是曝光控制的三个参数。\n\n但用户明确说了\"自动白平衡\"。让我再看看：\n\n> 自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在实际增益不是这么操作的。\n\n我觉得用户可能在说：局部亮度调整的初始值，应该从设备当前的光圈、快门、增益值开始。\n\n这更合理。因为亮度调整就是调光圈、快门、增益。如果初始值不从设备当前值读取，那调整就没有正确的起点。\n\n但router.py中：\n```python\nshutter_idx = int(data.get(\"shutter_idx\", 0))\niris_idx = int(data.get(\"iris_idx\", 0))\ngain = int(data.get(\"gain\", 50))\n```\n\n这些值从前端传入。如果前端传的是正确的当前值，那没问题。但用户说\"现在实际增益不是这么操作的\"，可能意味着初始值没有正确读取。\n\n让我看看BrightnessSearcher.run()方法：\n\n```python\nasync def run(self):\n    # 读取快门延迟\n    self._stable_delay = await asyncio.to_thread(calc_stable_delay, self.client)\n    \n    # 1. 切换手动曝光模式\n    await asyncio.to_thread(self._set_exposure_manual)\n    \n    # 2. 初始截图\n    bgr, info = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\n    ...\n```\n\n这里没有读取当前光圈/快门/增益。初始值是从构造函数传入的。\n\n现在回到问题1：增益震荡3次后应用最佳值，在增益步长为1时实现。\n\n看代码：\n```python\n# v8.68: 增益震荡检测 - 连续3次穿越目标 → 回滚最佳值并成功\ncurrent_side = 1 if current_brightness > self._target else -1\nif self._gain_last_side != 0 and current_side != self._gain_last_side:\n    self._gain_osc_count += 1\n    if self._gain_osc_count >= 3:\n        # 震荡3次，回滚到最佳增益\n        self._gain = self._best_gain_val\n        return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n            f\"增益震荡{self._gain_osc_count}次，回滚最佳增益{self._gain}\")\nself._gain_last_side = current_side\n```\n\n这里的问题是：这个检测在增益阶段就会执行，不管是在粗调还是精调。用户要求只在精调（步长=1）时检测。\n\n所以修复方案：\n1. 把震荡检测移到精调阶段\n2. 初始值从设备读取\n\n但用户说\"禁止过度开发\"，所以我需要：\n1. 修复问题1：只在精调时检测震荡\n2. 修复问题2：从设备读取初始值\n\n等等，让我再仔细读用户的要求：\n\n\"1. 我需要实现的，最终3次震荡3次后应用最佳，并且是在增益以1为步进的情况下实现，现在实际没有实现。\"\n\n这里说的是：在增益步长为1的情况下，检测3次震荡后应用最佳值。\n\n看代码，震荡检测确实存在，但问题可能是：\n- 检测在粗调和精调都会执行\n- 或者检测逻辑有问题\n\n看代码：\n```python\ncurrent_side = 1 if current_brightness > self._target else -1\nif self._gain_last_side != 0 and current_side != self._gain_last_side:\n    self._gain_osc_count += 1\n```\n\n这里每次穿越目标就+1。但问题是：这个检测在每次step()调用时都会执行，不管是在粗调还是精调。\n\n修复方案：只在精调时（`self._gain_phase == 2`）检测震荡。\n\n问题2：初始值从设备读取。\n\n看BrightnessSearcher.run()：\n```python\nasync def run(self):\n    # 读取快门延迟\n    self._stable_delay = await asyncio.to_thread(calc_stable_delay, self.client)\n    \n    # 1. 切换手动曝光模式\n    await asyncio.to_thread(self._set_exposure_manual)\n    \n    # 2. 初始截图\n    bgr, info = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\n    ...\n```\n\n这里没有读取当前光圈/快门/增益。但初始值是从构造函数传入的，从router.py传入。\n\n如果前端传的是正确的当前值，那没问题。但用户说\"现在实际增益不是这么操作的\"，可能意味着：\n- 前端传的值不对\n- 或者需要在后端读取当前值\n\n让我看看如何从设备读取当前值。我需要：\n1. 读取当前快门值 → 转换为shutter_idx\n2. 读取当前光圈值 → 转换为iris_idx\n3. 读取当前增益值\n\n这需要调用ISAPI接口。让我看看现有的代码是否有读取功能。\n\n看whitebalance.py中的`_read_wb_status()`：\n```python\ndef _read_wb_status(self):\n    \"\"\"读取当前白平衡状态（模式+增益）- v8.62\"\"\"\n    try:\n        resp = self.client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\")\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\n            import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n            mode = \"auto\"\n            red, blue = 100, 100\n            for elem in root.iter():\n                tag = elem.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in elem.tag else elem.tag\n                if tag in (\"WhiteBalanceStyle\", \"whiteBalanceStyle\"):\n                    mode = (elem.text or \"auto\").lower()\n                elif tag in (\"WhiteBalanceRed\", \"whiteBalanceRed\"):\n                    red = int(elem.text)\n                elif tag in (\"WhiteBalanceBlue\", \"whiteBalanceBlue\"):\n                    blue = int(elem.text)\n            return mode, red, blue\n    except:\n        pass\n    return \"auto\", 100, 100\n```\n\n类似地，我需要在brightness.py中添加读取当前曝光参数的方法。\n\n让我看看ISAPI接口：\n- 快门：`/Image/channels/1/Shutter` → `<ShutterLevel>...</ShutterLevel>`\n- 光圈：`/Image/channels/1/Iris` → `<IrisLevel>...</IrisLevel>`\n- 增益：`/Image/channels/1/gain` → `<GainLevel>...</GainLevel>`\n\n但这些返回的是字符串，需要转换为索引。\n\n现在，我需要：\n1. 在BrightnessSearcher中添加读取方法\n2. 在run()中读取当前值并更新初始值\n3. 修复震荡检测，只在精调时执行\n\n让我开始修复。\n\n等等，用户说\"修复完成向我报告\"。我需要先修复，然后报告。\n\n让我先修复问题1：震荡检测只在精调时执行。\n\n看代码：\n```python\n# === 优先级3: 增益 ===\n# v8.68: 增益震荡检测 - 连续3次穿越目标 → 回滚最佳值并成功\ncurrent_side = 1 if current_brightness > self._target else -1\nif self._gain_last_side != 0 and current_side != self._gain_last_side:\n    self._gain_osc_count += 1\n    if self._gain_osc_count >= 3:\n        # 震荡3次，回滚到最佳增益\n        self._gain = self._best_gain_val\n        return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n            f\"增益震荡{self._gain_osc_count}次，回滚最佳增益{self._gain}\")\nself._gain_last_side = current_side\n```\n\n修复：只在`self._gain_phase == 2`时检测。\n\n```python\n# === 优先级3: 增益 ===\n# v8.70: 增益震荡检测 - 只在精调阶段（步长=1）检测\nif self._gain_phase == 2:\n    current_side = 1 if current_brightness > self._target else -1\n    if self._gain_last_side != 0 and current_side != self._gain_last_side:\n        self._gain_osc_count += 1\n        if self._gain_osc_count >= 3:\n            # 震荡3次，回滚到最佳增益\n            self._gain = self._best_gain_val\n            return self._make_stop_result(\"done\", current_brightness,\n                f\"增益震荡{self._gain_osc_count}次，回滚最佳增益{self._gain}\")\n    self._gain_last_side = current_side\n```\n\n问题2：从设备读取初始值。\n\n我需要在BrightnessSearcher.run()中添加读取当前曝光参数的代码。\n\n让我先添加读取方法：\n\n```python\ndef _read_current_exposure(self):\n    \"\"\"读取当前曝光参数（快门、光圈、增益）\"\"\"\n    try:\n        # 读取快门\n        resp = self.client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\n            import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n            for elem in root.iter():\n                tag = elem.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in elem.tag else elem.tag\n                if tag in (\"ShutterLevel\", \"shutterLevel\"):\n                    shutter_level = elem.text\n                    # 转换为索引\n                    if shutter_level in self._shutter_values:\n                        self._shutter_idx = self._shutter_values.index(shutter_level)\n        \n        # 读取光圈\n        resp = self.client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Iris\")\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\n            import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n            for elem in root.iter():\n                tag = elem.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in elem.tag else elem.tag\n                if tag in (\"IrisLevel\", \"irisLevel\"):\n                    iris_level = elem.text\n                    # 转换为索引\n                    if iris_level in self._iris_values:\n                        self._iris_idx = self._iris_values.index(iris_level)\n        \n        # 读取增益\n        resp = self.client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/gain\")\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\n            import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n            for elem in root.iter():\n                tag = elem.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in elem.tag else elem.tag\n                if tag in (\"GainLevel\", \"gainLevel\"):\n                    gain_level = int(elem.text)\n                    self._gain = min(self._gain_max, max(self._gain_min, gain_level))\n    except:\n        pass\n```\n\n然后在run()中调用：\n\n```python\nasync def run(self):\n    # 读取当前曝光参数\n    await asyncio.to_thread(self._read_current_exposure)\n    \n    # 读取快门延迟\n    self._stable_delay = await asyncio.to_thread(calc_stable_delay, self.client)\n    \n    # 1. 切换手动曝光模式\n    await asyncio.to_thread(self._set_exposure_manual)\n    ...\n```\n\n等等，这里有个问题。用户说\"自动白平衡的初始值\" — 但白平衡和白平衡搜索是不同的。让我再仔细读：\n\n\"自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在实际增益不是这么操作的。\"\n\n我理解错了。用户可能在说：\n- 白平衡搜索时，需要先固定曝光参数（光圈、快门、增益）\n- 白平衡搜索的初始值应该是当前的光圈、快门、增益\n\n但白平衡搜索是调R/B增益，和光圈快门增益无关。\n\n哦！我想明白了。用户可能在说\"自动曝光\"（不是白平衡）。因为光圈、快门、增益是曝光控制的三个参数。\n\n让我重新理解：\n\"自动曝光的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始。现在实际增益不是这么操作的。\"\n\n这意味着：亮度调整（自动曝光）应该从当前的光圈、快门、增益值开始。\n\n这更合理。因为亮度调整就是调光圈、快门、增益。如果初始值不从设备当前值读取，那调整就没有正确的起点。\n\n让我继续修复。\n\n等等，让我再仔细看代码。BrightnessSearcher的初始值是从构造函数传入的：\n\n```python\ndef __init__(self, mgr, device_ip, client, x, y, w, h, capture_func,\n             cleanup_func, target, shutter_idx, iris_idx, gain,\n             shutter_values, iris_values, gain_min=0, gain_max=100,\n             mac_clean=\"\"):\n    ...\n    self._shutter_idx = shutter_idx\n    self._iris_idx = iris_idx\n    self._gain = gain\n    ...\n```\n\n这些值从router.py传入：\n\n```python\nshutter_idx = int(data.get(\"shutter_idx\", 0))\niris_idx = int(data.get(\"iris_idx\", 0))\ngain = int(data.get(\"gain\", 50))\n\nsearcher = BrightnessSearcher(\n    mgr=mgr, device_ip=device_ip, client=client,\n    x=x, y=y, w=w, h=h,\n    capture_func=_capture_and_crop,\n    cleanup_func=_cleanup_temp,\n    mac_clean=connected.get(\"mac\", \"\").replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower(),\n    target=target, shutter_idx=shutter_idx, iris_idx=iris_idx,\n    gain=gain, shutter_values=shutter_values, iris_values=iris_values,\n    gain_min=gain_min, gain_max=gain_max\n)\n```\n\n所以初始值是从前端传入的。如果前端传的是正确的当前值，那没问题。但用户说\"现在实际增益不是这么操作的\"，可能意味着：\n- 前端传的值不对\n- 或者需要在后端读取当前值\n\n让我在后端添加读取当前值的代码。\n\n现在让我编写修复代码。\n\n修复1：震荡检测只在精调时执行\n修复2：从设备读取初始值\n\n让我开始编辑brightness.py。\n老板，我现在修复两个问题。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_82103efbced7432d8eadae85","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # === 优先级3: 