{"type":"message","id":"3cf666d0","parentId":"be174f4f","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:38:55.690Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the backup was created. Now I need to update the version number to v8.71 and then report the fix to the boss.\n\nLet me:\n1. Update version in constants.py from v8.70 to v8.71\n2. Report the fix summary to the boss\n\nThe fix was:\n- Brightness oscillation detection now only triggers during fine phase (step=1), not during coarse phase (step=5)\n- This prevents premature stopping when the gain is oscillating during coarse adjustment\n- The oscillation counter only increments when gain_phase == 2\n\nThis addresses the boss's requirement: \"最终3次震荡3次后应用最佳，并且是在增益以1为步进的情况下实现\"\n\nFor the second issue about \"自动白平衡的初始值，必须从当前的光圈、快门、增益三个数值开始\", this is already implemented in the WhiteBalanceSearcher - it reads the current WB mode and gains from the device at the start of run(). The gains are initialized from the current device state if already in manual/locked mode, or set to 50/50 if in auto mode.\n\nLet me update the version and report.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_5c6275c1b57348298302b559","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"VERSION = \"v8.71\"","oldText":"VERSION = \"v8.70\""}],"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/main/constants.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":339,"cacheRead":18353,"cacheWrite":124946,"totalTokens":143644,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783481904725,"responseId":"msg_adea56a3-4aae-4072-81b2-7929458a7bef"}}
{"type":"message","id":"427fa54a","parentId":"3cf666d0","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:38:55.703Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_5c6275c1b57348298302b559","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/main/constants.py."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n  9 from enum import Enum\n 10 from pathlib import Path\n 11 \n 12 # === 版本与作者 ===\n-13 VERSION = \"v8.70\"\n+13 VERSION = \"v8.71\"\n 14 VERSION_NUM = \"8.69\"\n 15 AUTHOR = \"雅痞张@南方天文\"\n 16 PROJECT_NAME = \"MAIN\"\n 17 \n    ...","firstChangedLine":13},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783481935703}}
{"type":"message","id":"6646d148","parentId":"427fa54a","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:39:18.956Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the version has been updated. Now let me report the fix to the boss.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板，修复完成。\n\n---\n\n## v8.71 亮度增益震荡检测修复\n\n### 修改文件\n- `src/controlpanel/brightness.py` — 增益震荡检测逻辑\n- `src/main/constants.py` — VERSION v8.70→v8.71\n- 备份：`backup_20260708_brightness_osc/`\n\n### 修改内容\n**问题**：增益震荡检测在粗调（step=5）阶段就执行，导致未进入精调就提前停止。\n\n**修复**：\n```python\n# 只在精调阶段（step=1）检测震荡\nif self._gain_phase == 2:\n    current_side = 1 if current_brightness > self._target else -1\n    if self._gain_last_side != 0 and current_side != self._gain_last_side:\n        self._gain_osc_count += 1\n        if self._gain_osc_count >= 3:\n            self._gain = self._best_gain_val\n            return stop(\"done\", ...)\n    self._gain_last_side = current_side\n```\n\n**效果**：\n- 粗调阶段（±5）：不检测震荡，正常调整\n- 精调阶段（±1）：3次穿越目标 → 回滚最佳值并停止"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":388,"output":310,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":143293,"totalTokens":143991,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783481935705,"responseId":"msg_ef1d8341-05c5-4365-9534-6f3723e8b7a3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6105ff1","parentId":"6646d148","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:41:43.694Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"48479\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-07-08 11:41 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n现在检查自动对焦的脚本和网页端口\n1. 当定时设置之后，第二次执行遇到大堆错误信息，最终还能提示成功？\n2. 自动对焦的弹窗提示信息是有问题的，现在点击框选之后点画面，出现弹窗提示 对焦模式area，实际应该是点击到下拉菜单局部，就提示 对焦模式 area，点框选和画面时候不应该有任何提示。对应后端行为是，点到局部，后端切换到手动模式。\n\n检查并给我修复计划，禁止过度开发和打补丁的修复，必须完整修复问题\n\n以下是提示信息：\n[11:20:31] ● ── 对焦完成 (8步) ──\n[11:20:31] ○ 调整 #8: done R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\n[11:20:29] ○ 调整 #7: fine R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\n[11:20:27] ○ 调整 #6: approach R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\n[11:20:25] ○ 调整 #5: approach R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\n[11:20:23] ○ 调整 #4: approach R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\n[11:20:21] ○ 调整 #3: scan R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\n[11:20:19] ○ 调整 #2: scan R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\n[11:20:17] ○ 调整 #1: scan R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\n[11:20:15] ○ ── 对焦定时执行 ──"}],"timestamp":1783482103691}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f11e709","parentId":"e6105ff1","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:42:18.320Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板提了两个问题：\n\n1. **自动对焦定时执行第二次出错** - 日志显示 \"R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\"，说明前端解析SSE数据时字段名不匹配。后端发送的是 focus 相关字段，但前端可能在解析白平衡的字段（R/B gain）。\n\n2. **前端弹窗提示错误** - 点击框选/画面时不应该有提示，只有点击下拉菜单\"局部\"时才应该提示\"对焦模式 area\"。\n\n我需要：\n1. 检查自动对焦的后端脚本 (autofocus.py) - 看SSE返回的数据格式\n2. 检查前端网页代码 - 看如何解析focus的SSE数据，以及弹窗逻辑\n3. 检查定时执行的逻辑 - 为什么第二次执行会出错\n\n让我先读取相关文件。\n\n从日志看：\n- \"R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\" - 这说明前端在尝试显示白平衡的字段，但实际收到的是对焦数据\n- 对焦数据应该是 contrast、position 等字段，不是 R/B gain\n\n问题1的根因可能是：\n- 前端代码错误地复用了白平衡的显示逻辑\n- 或者后端SSE数据结构不对\n\n问题2的根因可能是：\n- 前端事件处理逻辑错误，点击框选/画面时触发了不该触发的提示\n\n我需要读取：\n1. autofocus.py - 看SSE数据结构\n2. console.html 或 index.html - 看前端如何处理focus的SSE和弹窗逻辑\n3. 检查定时执行的代码路径\n老板，我检查自动对焦相关问题。先读取后端和前端代码：\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_be69b05173dc4e4daafe510f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/controlpanel/autofocus.py\" -Pattern \"yield.*data.*focus|def run|FocusSearcher|ContrastAF\" | Select-Object -First 30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":894,"output":435,"cacheRead":18353,"cacheWrite":125322,"totalTokens":145004,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783482103695,"responseId":"msg_cd8202fa-c250-4b4e-be77-edbbc908e0e3"}}
