{"type":"message","id":"7b70616c","parentId":"2a2cde35","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:42:46.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is reporting two issues with the autofocus script:\n\n1. When executing autofocus a second time (after scheduling), there are lots of errors but it still shows success. The log shows \"R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\" which suggests the frontend is trying to display white balance fields (R, B, delta) for a focus operation, which doesn't make sense.\n\n2. The popup message for autofocus mode is incorrect - when clicking on \"frame selection\" or \"image\", it shows \"focus mode area\" popup, but it should only show this when clicking the dropdown menu to \"local\" mode.\n\nLet me read the autofocus.py file to understand the FocusSearcher class and its SSE event structure, then check the frontend code to understand the popup logic.\n\nThe log shows:\n```\n[11:20:31] ● ── 对焦完成 (8步) ──\n[11:20:31] ○ 调整 #8: done R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\n...\n```\n\nThis suggests the frontend is trying to display R, B, and delta fields from the focus SSE events, but the focus events don't have these fields. Let me check what fields the focus events actually send.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_394af7e021a14b76acb22317","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":709,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/controlpanel/autofocus.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":344,"cacheRead":143299,"cacheWrite":1835,"totalTokens":145484,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783482138790,"responseId":"msg_8a6ae1e6-ac1e-403b-a7b2-23f4381dfd7f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cab826e5","parentId":"7b70616c","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:42:46.874Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_394af7e021a14b76acb22317","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    async def run(self):\r\n        \"\"\"运行对焦搜索，产生 SSE 事件。\"\"\"\r\n\r\n        # v8.64: 快门延迟只读一次\r\n        self._stable_delay = await asyncio.to_thread(calc_stable_delay, self.client)\r\n\r\n        # 1. 设置手动对焦\r\n        ok = await asyncio.to_thread(self._set_manual_focus)\r\n        if not ok:\r\n            yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'warning', 'message': '设置手动对焦失败'})}\\n\\n\"\r\n\r\n        # 2. 初始截图\r\n        bgr, info = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\r\n        if bgr is None:\r\n            yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '截图失败'})}\\n\\n\"\r\n            return\r\n\r\n        crop_msg = f\"X={info['crop_x1']}~{info['crop_x2']}, Y={info['crop_y1']}~{info['crop_y2']}, 共{info['pixels']}像素\"\r\n        yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'start', 'crop': crop_msg})}\\n\\n\"\r\n\r\n        # 3. 对焦循环\r\n        af = ContrastAF()\r\n        step_count = 0\r\n\r\n        while True:\r\n            # v8.41: 检查中断\r\n            if self._interrupted:\r\n                await asyncio.to_thread(self._stop_focus)\r\n                yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'interrupt', 'message': '用户停止'})}\\n\\n\"\r\n                break\r\n\r\n            contrast = calc_contrast(bgr)\r\n            cmd = af.step(contrast)\r\n            step_count += 1\r\n\r\n            event = {\r\n                \"type\": \"focus\",\r\n                \"step\": step_count,\r\n                \"stage\": cmd.get(\"stage\", \"\"),\r\n                \"action\": cmd[\"action\"],\r\n                \"contrast\": cmd[\"contrast\"],\r\n                \"duration\": cmd[\"duration\"],\r\n                \"message\": cmd[\"message\"]\r\n            }\r\n            yield f\"data: {json.dumps(event)}\\n\\n\"\r\n\r\n            if cmd[\"action\"] == \"stop\":\r\n                # 验证\r\n                bgr2, _ = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\r\n                final_contrast = calc_contrast(bgr2) if bgr2 is not None else cmd[\"contrast\"]\r\n                best = cmd.get(\"best\", cmd[\"contrast\"])\r\n                verified = final_contrast >= best * 0.95\r\n\r\n                yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'done', 'final_contrast': round(final_contrast, 2), 'best_contrast': round(best, 2), 'total_steps': step_count, 'verified': verified})}\\n\\n\"\r\n                break\r\n\r\n            # 移动\r\n            await asyncio.to_thread(self._move_focus, cmd[\"action\"], cmd[\"duration\"])\r\n            await asyncio.sleep(cmd[\"duration\"])\r\n            await asyncio.to_thread(self._stop_focus)\r\n            await asyncio.sleep(self._stable_delay)  # v8.64: 等待稳定（快门缓存）\r\n\r\n            # 重新截图\r\n            bgr, _ = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\r\n            if bgr is None:\r\n                await asyncio.to_thread(self._stop_focus)\r\n                yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '截图失败'})}\\n\\n\"\r\n                break\r\n\r\n        # 4. 清理\r\n        await asyncio.to_thread(self._cleanup_func, \"Focus\", self.device_ip)\r\n        yield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'cleanup'})}\\n\\n\"\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783482166874}}
{"type":"message","id":"e77c6bde","parentId":"cab826e5","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:43:11.837Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我现在明白了问题 1。SSE 事件发送的是 `type: \"focus\"`，包含 `contrast`、`duration`、`stage`、`action`、`message` 等字段。但日志显示 `R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined`，这意味着前端在渲染 focus 事件时使用了白平衡字段（R、B、Δ）。这表明前端针对这两种类型使用了相同的渲染逻辑。\n\n让我检查一下前端代码，看看 focus 事件是如何渲染的，以及定时搜索逻辑是如何运作的。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_14d67c459e48468c9aa2079d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/index.html\",\"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html\" -Pattern \"对焦|focus.*search|focus.*mode|focusMode|focus_mode\" -Context 2,2 | Select-Object -First 60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":129840,"output":204,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130044,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783482166876,"responseId":"cht000dd5e9@dx19f3fd26b3d29bb503"}}
