{"type":"message","id":"dc39357a","parentId":"d2b16863","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:43:45.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has reported two issues with the autofocus feature:\n\n1. **When scheduled (定时设置之后), second execution shows errors but still reports success** - The log shows `R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined` for focus events. This means the frontend is displaying fields that don't exist for focus events (R, B, delta are white balance fields). The frontend code is likely using the same display logic for both white balance and focus events.\n\n2. **Popup message timing is wrong** - When clicking the area selection or image, it shows \"对焦模式 area\" popup, but it should only show this when clicking the dropdown \"local\" option. The corresponding backend behavior is: when clicking \"local\", switch to manual mode.\n\nLet me search for the relevant frontend code to understand the issue better.\n\nFrom the grep results, I can see:\n- `toggleRegionMode('focus')` calls `setFocusMode('area')` \n- `onFocusModeChange(mode)` is the function that handles mode changes\n- There's a `focusMode` select element with options \"auto\", \"manual\"\n\nThe issue seems to be that when clicking on the image to select an area (框选), the code is triggering the focus mode change popup. Let me look at the specific code:\n\nFrom the grep:\n```javascript\n// v8.60: 框选时切换设备模式\nif (mode === 'focus') {\n    setFocusMode('area');\n}\n```\n\nAnd:\n```javascript\nfunction onFocusModeChange(mode) {\n    var moveControls = document.getElementById('focusMoveControls');\n    var localControls = document.getElementById('focusLocalControls');\n```\n\nThe `onFocusModeChange` function seems to handle the UI changes when the focus mode changes. It's called both when the dropdown changes and when the area is selected.\n\nThe issue is that `setFocusMode('area')` is being called when clicking on the image (框选), but the popup message should only show when selecting \"local\" from the dropdown menu, not when clicking on the image.\n\nLet me read more of the code to understand the full flow.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:45","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/index.html\" -Pattern \"setFocusMode\\('area'\\)|toggleRegionMode\\('focus'\\)\" -Context 3,3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":136723,"output":509,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137232,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783482192322,"responseId":"cht000d4104@dx19f3fd2b11f2871503"}}
