{"type":"message","id":"d91c1c61","parentId":"27378205","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:44:01.023Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has two issues to investigate:\n\n1. When scheduled focus search runs for the second time, it shows errors but still reports success. The log shows `R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined` which means the frontend is trying to display fields that don't exist for focus events (it's using white balance fields R, B, delta instead of focus-specific fields like contrast, action, duration).\n\n2. The popup message for autofocus mode is incorrect. When clicking on the area selection button or image, it shouldn't show any popup. Only when selecting \"area\" from the dropdown should it show \"对焦模式 area\". Currently clicking frame select or image triggers the popup.\n\nLet me read the relevant code more carefully.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_90b22337b0644fdb8dc0daea","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":2850,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":224,"cacheRead":145134,"cacheWrite":8483,"totalTokens":153847,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783482226350,"responseId":"msg_07fe9b34-1328-4e4d-a17c-8df532548308"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3fa0f26b","parentId":"d91c1c61","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:44:01.030Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_90b22337b0644fdb8dc0daea","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    var _regionMode = null;\r\n    var _regionStartX = 0, _regionStartY = 0;\r\n\r\n    function toggleRegionMode(mode) {\r\n        // 新的按钮 ID（在白平衡/对焦局部控制中）\r\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\r\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnFocusRegionSelect');\r\n        var btnBright = document.getElementById('btnBrightRegionSelect');\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        if (_regionMode === mode) {\r\n            _regionMode = null;\r\n            if (btnWB) btnWB.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            if (btnAF) btnAF.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            if (btnBright) btnBright.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            overlay.style.display = 'none';\r\n            box.style.display = 'none';\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n            showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        // v8.39: 移除手动模式限制 - 局部模式自动切换到手动\r\n        // 当选择局部框选时，自动切换到手动模式\r\n        if (mode === 'whitebalance') {\r\n            var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n            if (wbMode && wbMode.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                // 自动切换到手动模式\r\n                setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        // v8.60: 点击框选时才切换设备模式\r\n        if (mode === 'focus') {\r\n            setFocusMode('area');\r\n        }\r\n        _regionMode = mode;\r\n        if (btnWB) btnWB.className = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        if (btnAF) btnAF.className = mode === 'focus' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        if (btnBright) btnBright.className = mode === 'brightness' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        overlay.style.display = 'block';\r\n        box.style.display = 'none';\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function _getOverlayPos(e) {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var rect = overlay.getBoundingClientRect();\r\n        return { x: e.clientX - rect.left, y: e.clientY - rect.top };\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    // v8.11: 统一 ISAPI 截图 → 后端裁剪 → 迭代搜索 → 操作日志\r\n    function _finishRegion() {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        var dev = window.connectedDevice;\r\n        if (!dev || !dev.ip) { showToast('error', '未连接设备'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var ow = overlay.offsetWidth, oh = overlay.offsetHeight;\r\n        var sx = parseInt(box.style.left) / ow;\r\n        var sy = parseInt(box.style.top) / oh;\r\n\n[220 more lines in file. Use offset=2910 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783482241030}}
{"type":"message","id":"50585194","parentId":"3fa0f26b","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:44:14.666Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_98a98173952247a68510a873","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":2910,"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":137579,"output":44,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137623,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783482241033,"responseId":"cht000d5cea@dx19f3fd3576c29c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"60fc8702","parentId":"50585194","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:44:14.672Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_98a98173952247a68510a873","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        var sw = parseInt(box.style.width) / ow;\r\n        var sh = parseInt(box.style.height) / oh;\r\n        if (sw < 0.01 || sh < 0.01) { showToast('warning', '框选区域太小'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var mode = _regionMode;\r\n        \r\n        // v8.39: 保存选区到 localStorage（白平衡和对焦分别保存）\r\n        var regionKey = 'region_' + mode;\r\n        localStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));\r\n        \r\n        var endpoint = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search'\r\n                       : mode === 'brightness' ? '/api/v1/vision/brightness-search'\r\n                       : '/api/v1/vision/focus-search';\r\n        var label = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '白平衡' : mode === 'brightness' ? '亮度' : '对焦';\r\n\r\n        _resetRegionUI();\r\n        showToast('info', label + '迭代中...');\r\n        operationLog('── ' + label + '迭代开始 ──', 'info');\r\n        \r\n        // v8.66: 流程开始，暂停主控台轮询\r\n        pausePtzPolling();\r\n\r\n        // v8.41: 搜索启动时启用停止按钮\r\n        var stopBtnId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btnWbLocalStop'\r\n                       : mode === 'brightness' ? 'btnBrightnessLocalStop'\r\n                       : 'btnFocusLocalStop';\r\n        var stopBtn = document.getElementById(stopBtnId);\r\n        if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = false; stopBtn.style.opacity = '1'; }\r\n\r\n        // SSE 流式调用\r\n        var body;\r\n        if (mode === 'brightness') {\r\n            var target = window.localBrightnessTarget || 50;\r\n            var shutterValues = (deviceFunctionData && deviceFunctionData.functions && deviceFunctionData.functions.shutter) ? deviceFunctionData.functions.shutter.opt_values : [];\r\n            var irisValues = (deviceFunctionData && deviceFunctionData.functions && deviceFunctionData.functions.iris) ? deviceFunctionData.functions.iris.opt_values : [];\r\n            var shutterIdx = 0;\r\n            if (deviceImageParams.shutter && deviceImageParams.shutter.current_level) {\r\n                shutterIdx = shutterValues.indexOf(String(deviceImageParams.shutter.current_level));\r\n                if (shutterIdx < 0) shutterIdx = 0;\r\n            }\r\n            var irisIdx = 0;\r\n            if (deviceImageParams.iris && deviceImageParams.iris.current_level) {\r\n                irisIdx = irisValues.indexOf(String(deviceImageParams.iris.current_level));\r\n                if (irisIdx < 0) irisIdx = 0;\r\n            }\r\n            var gainVal = (deviceImageParams.gain && deviceImageParams.gain.current_level) || 0;\r\n            body = JSON.stringify({\r\n                x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh,\r\n                target: target,\r\n                shutter_idx: shutterIdx,\r\n                iris_idx: irisIdx,\r\n                gain: gainVal,\r\n                shutter_values: shutterValues,\r\n                iris_values: irisValues,\r\n                gain_min: 0,\r\n                gain_max: (deviceImageParams.gain && deviceImageParams.gain.limit) || 100\r\n            });\r\n        } else {\r\n            body = JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh });\r\n        }\r\n        fetch(endpoint, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: body })\r\n            .then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (!resp.ok) throw new Error('HTTP ' + resp.status);\r\n                var reader = resp.body.getReader();\r\n                var decoder = new TextDecoder();\r\n                var buf = '';\r\n                function pump() {\r\n                    return reader.read().then(function(r) {\r\n                        if (r.done) return;\r\n                        buf += decoder.decode(r.value, { stream: true });\r\n                        // 按 \\n\\n 分割事件\r\n                        var parts = buf.split('\\n\\n');\r\n                        buf = parts.pop();  // 最后一段可能不完整\r\n                        for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {\r\n                            var line = parts[i];\r\n                            if (!line.startsWith('data: ')) continue;\r\n                            try {\r\n                                var ev = JSON.parse(line.slice(6));\r\n                                if (ev.type === 'start') {\r\n                                    operationLog(label + '开始, ' + ev.crop, 'info');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'wb') {\r\n                                    operationLog('调整 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage\r\n                                        + ' R=' + ev.red_gain + ' B=' + ev.blue_gain\r\n                                        + ' → R=' + ev.r_avg + ' G=' + ev.g_avg + ' B=' + ev.b_avg\r\n                                        + ' (Δ=' + ev.delta + ')', 'debug');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'focus') {\r\n                                    operationLog('对焦 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage\r\n                                        + ' ' + ev.action + ' 反差=' + ev.contrast\r\n                                        + ' (' + ev.duration + 's) ' + ev.message, 'debug');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'brightness') {\r\n                                    operationLog('亮度 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.message\r\n                                        + ' 快门=' + ev.shutter + ' 光圈=' + ev.iris\r\n                                        + ' 增益=' + ev.gain + ' 亮度=' + ev.brightness\r\n                                        + '/' + ev.target, 'debug');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'done') {\r\n                                    if (ev.final_red !== undefined) {\r\n                                        showToast('success', label + '完成 R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue);\r\n                                        operationLog('── ' + label + '完成: R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue + ' (' + ev.total_steps + '步) ──', 'success');\r\n                                        // 刷新主控台白平衡滑动条\r\n                                        var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n\n[120 more lines in file. Use offset=3010 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783482254672}}
{"type":"message","id":"7db86710","parentId":"60fc8702","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:44:37.159Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to check the focus search code and web console. They reported two issues:\n\n1. When timer is set and executes the second time, there are lots of error messages but it still shows success. The log shows \"R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\" for all steps.\n\n2. The popup message for focus mode is wrong. When clicking on area selection or the image, it shows \"focus mode area\" popup. But it should only show this when selecting \"local\" from the dropdown. The corresponding backend behavior is: when clicking local, it should switch to manual mode.\n\nLooking at the log:\n```\n[11:20:31] ● ── 对焦完成 (8步) ──\n[11:20:31] ○ 调整 #8: done R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\n[11:20:29] ○ 调整 #7: fine R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\n\n\n```\n\nI can see the problem now. The log is displaying focus steps but showing \"R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined\" instead of contrast values. Looking at the operationLog function around line 2996, it's logging focus events with ev.stage and ev.contrast, but somehow the undefined values are appearing in the output. This suggests the focus event handler isn't properly extracting the contrast data, or there's a mismatch between what the API returns and what the log function expects.\n\nI need to trace through how the timer calls executeScheduledSearch('focus') and examine both the backend response and frontend handling for scheduled focus searches to understand where the data is getting lost or malformed.\n\n```\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在深入检查问题1：定时执行时的SSE处理和日志显示\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_6439c402f5424e9c85db0242","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html\" -Pattern \"executeScheduledSearch|focus.*timer|scheduled.*focus\" -Context 5,30 | Select-Object -First 80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":460,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":156045,"totalTokens":156511,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783482254674,"responseId":"msg_9fa37ecc-8ce1-4874-984e-b2b235d51d22"}}
