{"type":"message","id":"5bf53d20","parentId":"438c9cd2","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:53:04.195Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to execute the fix plan I described. Let me review what needs to be fixed:\n\n**Problem 1**: `executeScheduledSearch()` in console.html uses wrong SSE log format for focus events. It shows R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined because it uses white balance log format for focus events.\n\n**Problem 2**: `toggleRegionMode('focus')` in index.html incorrectly calls `setFocusMode('area')`, causing a popup toast when clicking the area selection button.\n\nI need to:\n1. Fix console.html - add proper focus/brightness log branches in executeScheduledSearch()\n2. Fix index.html - remove setFocusMode('area') from toggleRegionMode('focus')\n\nLet me first read the relevant code sections to make precise edits.\n\nFor console.html, I need to find executeScheduledSearch() and look at how it handles SSE events. From the earlier search results, I saw it processes SSE events but might not have proper focus/brightness branches.\n\nFor index.html, I need to find toggleRegionMode('focus') and remove the setFocusMode('area') call.\n\nLet me read these sections carefully.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板，执行两个前端修复：\n\n1. `console.html` — `executeScheduledSearch()` 添加 focus/brightness 日志分支\n2. `index.html` — `toggleRegionMode('focus')` 移除 `setFocusMode('area')`\n\n先读取精确位置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:52","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html\" -Pattern \"executeScheduledSearch\" -Context 2,2"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:53","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/web/index.html\" -Pattern \"toggleRegionMode\\('focus'\\)|setFocusMode\\('area'\\)\" -Context 3,3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":158220,"output":414,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":158634,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783482749879,"responseId":"cht000d5b89@dx19f3fdb53b42872503"}}
