{"type":"message","id":"436c0eb1","parentId":"036606f9","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:55:29.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求执行修改，我已经完成了两个修改：\n\n1. `console.html` - 修复了 `executeScheduledSearch()` 中的 SSE 日志显示，将 focus 类型从白平衡格式分离出来，使用正确的对焦日志格式\n2. `index.html` - 移除了 `toggleRegionMode('focus')` 中的 `setFocusMode('area')` 调用，这样点击框选按钮时不会弹出\"对焦模式: area\"的提示\n\n现在需要向老板报告完成情况。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板，修复完成。\n\n---\n\n## 修改内容\n\n### 1. `index.html` — 移除框选时的模式切换\n**问题**：点击框选按钮时调用 `setFocusMode('area')`，触发 toast 提示\"对焦模式: area\"\n\n**修复**：删除 `toggleRegionMode('focus')` 中的 `setFocusMode('area')` 调用\n\n### 2. `console.html` — 修复定时对焦日志显示\n**问题**：`executeScheduledSearch()` 中 focus 事件用了白平衡的日志格式（R=undefined B=undefined）\n\n**修复**：\n```javascript\n// 修复前\nif (ev.type === 'wb' || ev.type === 'focus') {\n    operationLog('调整 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage + ' R=' + ev.red_gain + ' B=' + ev.blue_gain + ' Δ=' + ev.delta, 'info');\n}\n\n// 修复后\nif (ev.type === 'wb') {\n    operationLog('调整 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage + ' R=' + ev.red_gain + ' B=' + ev.blue_gain + ' Δ=' + ev.delta, 'info');\n} else if (ev.type === 'focus') {\n    operationLog('对焦 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage + ' ' + ev.action + ' 反差=' + ev.contrast + ' (' + ev.duration + 's) ' + ev.message, 'info');\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 预期效果\n\n| 场景 | 修复前 | 修复后 |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| 点击框选按钮 | 弹出\"对焦模式: area\" | 无弹窗，直接进入框选 |\n| 定时对焦日志 | `R=undefined B=undefined Δ=undefined` | `对焦 #1: scan focus-near 反差=123.4 (0.2s) 开始对焦...` |"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":143044,"output":539,"cacheRead":138240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":281823,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783482901464,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ca2ffd8f-23e5-9083-b527-c59de8ff67c0"}}
